            <li><strong>Completeness:</strong> Are all required documents present?</li>
            <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Do documents meet MOHRE requirements?</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            Hard blocks stop applications immediately. A passport with less than 6 months validity or a residency visa with less than 1 month remaining will not proceed past the first screen.
          </p>

          <h3>What Happens When Documents Are Missing</h3>

