            MOHRE uses a process called "Nawakas" (Arabic for "missing") to handle deficient applications. Unlike <a href="/blog/gdrfa-visa-document-problems/">GDRFA's generic rejection notices</a>, MOHRE's system is more specific. It identifies what is missing and provides a transaction tracking number.
          </p>

          <p>
