          </p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>No translation:</strong> Submitting documents only in English or another language</li>
            <li><strong>Foreign certification:</strong> Using a certified translation from your home country. MOHRE requires a UAE MOJ stamp, not a UK sworn translation or Indian notarized translation.</li>
            <li><strong>Translation before attestation:</strong> The same sequencing issue as <a href="/blog/gdrfa-visa-document-problems/">GDRFA applications</a>. Translate after attestation so the translation captures all stamps.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

