            <li><strong>Professional licenses:</strong> For regulated professions (medical, engineering, teaching)</li>
            <li><strong>Police clearance certificates:</strong> If required for your occupation category</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>What Does Not Need Translation</h3>

          <ul>
            <li>Passport (already bilingual or in English)</li>
            <li>Emirates ID (issued bilingually by ICP)</li>
            <li>Medical fitness certificate (issued bilingually in the UAE)</li>
            <li>Documents already in Arabic</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>The Employment Contract</h3>

