            <li><strong>Name mismatch:</strong> Request a translator's clarifying note. Consider a notarized name equivalency affidavit from your home country for significant differences.</li>
            <li><strong>Expired documents:</strong> Obtain fresh copies and restart the attestation-translation sequence.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Step 3: Resubmit Through Tasheel</h3>

          <p>
