            <li><strong>Experience letters:</strong> From each employer listed in your CV. Attested and translated if from a foreign employer.</li>
            <li><strong>Professional license:</strong> If your occupation is regulated (healthcare, engineering, teaching). Attested and translated.</li>
            <li><strong><a href="/personal/immigration/pcc/">Police clearance certificate:</a></strong> Within validity period. Attested and translated.</li>
